rows.label: qst610203_msg0002
rows.name:
So many treats! Such tasties!
Get in belly right now!!!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0004
rows.name: Oh dear, but me forget manners!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0005
rows.name:
Me am Jizo! And friends
are Jizo's saviors!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0006
rows.name:
Jizo come for Igna-watching, but
did not expect Igna so scary.
Jizo stiffen from fright...

rows.label: qst610203_msg0007
rows.name:
Was afraid, if Igna find, Jizo become lizard
snack, so stay very, very still. So still,
he gather dust, end up like statue...

rows.label: qst610203_msg0008
rows.name:
Then Jizo get so hungry, couldn't
move even if wanted to! ...Which he
didn't, for aforementioned reasons.

rows.label: qst610203_msg0009
rows.name:
So Jizo feel extreme thankful
that friends come and help
from goodness of hearts!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0010
rows.name:
Mo-mo! Jizo have no idea that Sumisumi
so worried! Jizo feel terrible!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0012
rows.name:
...Is maybe matter for later time.
For now, Jizo hurry and join this
Sumisumi in Guild of Avaritia!

rows.label: qst610203_msg0013
rows.name:
Jizo have enough "adventure"
for many-many lifetimes...

rows.label: qst610203_msg0014
rows.name:
Oh, Jizo also mention this! Jizo is
actually skilled craftsman who make
cylinders for when salvaging.

rows.label: qst610203_msg0015
rows.name:
When friends next come to Avaritia,
friends come to shop of Jizo.

rows.label: qst610203_msg0017
rows.name:
Jizo wait in Goldmund
Residential District,
yes-yes? See friends later!
